item.title: CVE-2019-1010018|2024-08-05T03:07:18.312Z -- zammad%20gmbh -- zammad
item.description: Zammad GmbH Zammad 2.3.0 and earlier is affected by: Cross Site Scripting (XSS) - CWE-80. The impact is: Execute java script code on users browser. The component is: web app. The attack vector is: the victim must open a ticket. The fixed version is: 2.3.1, 2.2.2 and 2.1.3.
